text:
Good work, Madoka.
Looks like you were working hard.

That was the only thing
I had to do.

Haha, I see. Seems like you were getting along
well with everyone around you, right?

You were practicing with Mikoto, right?
I'm glad you're getting along.

--Ah, I just came to check on you for a moment.
Didn't mean to disturb--

...Can I take a break soon?
I'm tired.
